超汶川地震！25633名逆行者驰援湖北保卫战！王贺胜：已开放9个方舱医院。
Wenchuan earthquake! 25633 inverse travelers to help Hubei defend the war! Wang He Sheng: has opened 9 cabin hospitals.
中国经营报                      。
