2月15日上午，国务院新闻办公室在湖北武汉举行新闻发布会，请国家卫生健康委党组成员、副主任，湖北省委常委王贺胜等介绍在湖北组织开展疫情防控和医疗救治工作情况，并答记者问。
On the morning of February 15, the State Council Information Office held a press conference in Wuhan, Hubei Province, and invited Wang He-sheng, a member and deputy director of the Party committee of the State Council of Health, to give an account of the prevention and control of the epidemic and medical treatment in Hubei Province.
此次调动医疗救援规模速度超汶川地震王贺胜介绍，截至2月14日14时，各地共派出了217支医疗队，25633名医疗队员（不含军队派出的医疗队和队员），还调集了三个移动的P3实验室。
As of 1400 hours on February 14, 217 medical teams had been dispatched, 25,633 medical personnel (excluding medical teams and members of the army) had been dispatched, and three mobile P3 laboratories had been mobilized.
其中在武汉市有181支医疗队，20374名医疗队员，在其他城市有36支医疗队，5259名医疗队员，这些都大大超过了2008年汶川特大地震医疗救援的调动规模速度。
Of these, 181 medical teams, 20,374 medical personnel, 36 medical teams and 5,259 medical personnel in other cities in Wuhan city greatly exceeded the scale of mobilization of medical aid for the Wenchuan earthquake in 2008.
已开放9个方舱医院，6960多张床位王贺胜介绍，目前，已经开放了9个方舱医院，有6960多张床位，在院患者达到了5606名。
Nine square-cabin hospitals have been opened, with more than 6,960 beds for Wang He-sheng, and nine have been opened, with more than 6,960 beds and 5,606 hospital patients.
下一步根据需要，我们要继续腾空医院部分的病房，征用部分场馆，改造为定点医院和方舱医院，确保已排查确诊的患者和疑似患者都能够得到集中收治，确保所有没有收治的患者人数清零。
As the next step, we will continue to vacate part of the hospital wards, expropriate some of the facilities and convert them into designated hospitals and squatter hospitals to ensure that patients and suspected patients are treated centrally and that the number of patients who are not treated is zero.
湖北过半确诊病例采取中医药治疗在答问环节，王贺胜表示，中西医结合救治患者是此次疫情救治的一大特色。
Hubei more than half of the confirmed cases of Chinese medicine in the answer session, Wang He-sheng said that the combination of Chinese and Western medicine treatment of patients is a major feature of the epidemic.
记者远程提问他透露，目前已经派出了3支国家中医医疗队，并且组织全国的中医药系统共同向湖北派出医疗队员，达到2220人。
The reporter asked questions remotely. He revealed that three Chinese medicine teams had been dispatched to Hubei, and that the Chinese medicine system had sent 2,220 medical personnel nationwide.
中医医疗队坚持中西医结合，突出中医药的特色，湖北省一半以上的确诊病例都使用了中医药治疗。
TCM medical teams adhere to the combination of Chinese and Western medicine, highlighting the characteristics of Chinese medicine, Hubei Province more than half of the confirmed cases have used Chinese medicine treatment.
中医药还积极参与了社区防控，为有需求的群众发放中药。
TCM has also actively participated in community control and distributed Chinese medicines to needy people.
“我们通过统筹中西医的资源，协同攻关、优势互补，努力提高治愈率，最大程度降低病死率，切实维护人民群众的生命安全和身体健康。
"By pooling the resources of Chinese and Western medicine, working together to overcome difficulties and complement each other, we strive to raise the cure rate, minimize the fatality rate and ensure the people's lives, safety and health.
”王贺胜说。
'said Wang.
湖北防控工作到了最吃紧的时候国家卫健委疫情应对处置工作专家组组长梁万年表示，除湖北外，全国其它省份新增确诊病例数从2月3日起的800多例下降到2月13日的300例以下。
In addition to Hubei province, the number of newly confirmed cases in other provinces dropped from more than 800 on February 3 to less than 300 on February 13, said Liang Wannian, chairman of the national health committee's expert group on epidemic prevention and treatment.
其中8个地区新增确诊病例人数连续3天小于5例，这是一个比较好的迹象。
In eight of these districts, the number of newly confirmed cases was less than five for three consecutive days, which is a good sign.
但武汉市每日新增确诊病例数仍处于较高水平，但2月1日以后处于下降趋势。
However, the daily number of newly confirmed cases in Wuhan city is still at a high level, but after February 1, it is in a downward trend.
湖北省其他地市中，有的地市发病水平依然高，如孝感、黄冈等。
In other cities in Hubei Province, some cities still have high levels of morbidity, such as filial piety, Huanggang and so on.
湖北防控工作到了最吃紧的时候，也是一种焦灼对垒的状态，要毫不放松地把疫情防控工作作为重中之重。
Hubei prevention and control work to the most tight time, but also a burning against the state, to let the disease control work as a top priority.
武汉市金银潭医院和肺科医院患者出院率达30%-39%国家卫健委医政医管局副局长焦雅辉介绍，以武汉市最早重症定点两家医院为例，金银潭医院和武汉肺科医院，他们现在患者的出院率已经达到了30%到39%，所以从这个数字来看，给我们带来了极大的信心。
According to Jiao Yahui, deputy director of the Hospital of Health Administration of Wuhan City, the first two hospitals in Wuhan, the gold and silver pool hospital and Wuhan lung hospital, the discharge rate of patients has reached 30% to 39%.
